column1: # This table of constellations was adapted from this list by P. Barber:
# Two additional commented-out entries at the end represent
# Serpens Cauda and Caput. Columns are:
# RA of constellation center is in decimal hours
# Dec of constellation center is in decimal degrees
# Area of constellation is in square degrees
# Rank is by area from largest (1) to smallest (88)
# Name is official IAU spelling of full Latin/Greek name
# Genitive is official IAU spelling of posessive form of name.
